<subSubSection pageId="10" pageNumber="301" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="10.[151,760,190,661]" pageId="10" pageNumber="301">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,276,542,565]" pageId="10" pageNumber="301">Etymology.</emphasis>
Named in honor of Warren E. Steiner, longtime friend and colleague, who has collected many new species of Neotropical 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Leach" authorityYear="1817" box="[311,427,606,629]" class="Insecta" family="Hydrochidae" genus="Hydrochus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="301" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[311,427,606,629]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="301">Hydrochus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, including the only known specimen of this species.
</paragraph>
